dil vil pyar &lt;unk&gt; ( english : heart vil pyar &lt;unk&gt; ) is a 2002 indian hindi romantic drama film written and directed by debutant director . the film features actors prosenjit chatterjee and namrata shirodkar in the lead roles . the film 's music is composed by r.d. burman . the film is a remake of the hindi film dil vil pyar diwani .